# New Tool Workflow

When adding a new tool integration (adapter/plugin/parser):

1) Use the scaffold in `docs/new_tool_template.md` as the starting point.
2) Follow `docs/new_tool_checklist.md` and ensure all applicable boxes are satisfied.
3) Do not invent a new structure. Conform to Somniosus architecture:
   - Adapters execute and save raw output.
   - Plugins orchestrate and write to state.
   - Parsers are deterministic and defensive.

Before finalizing a new tool PR/change:
- Summarize which checklist items were satisfied.
- Call out any checklist items intentionally skipped and why.
